---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'About — Meridian',
  description: 'Why Meridian was built — and how the team thinks about behavioral risk infrastructure for NinjaTrader 8 traders.',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-emerald-700 uppercase mb-4">Why Meridian Was Built</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 leading-snug">
        We built the tool we wished existed.
      </h1>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
        <p>
          Most trading software is built by engineers who have never traded, or by traders who outsource the engineering. Meridian sits at the intersection — built by traders who learned to ship software because no one else was going to build this.
        </p>
        <p>
          The frustration that started Meridian was simple: every existing risk tool fires <em>after</em> the damage. Daily loss limit hits at -$500 — by then the revenge trade has already happened. A trade journal shows the pattern at 8pm — the next morning the same thing happens again.
        </p>
        <p>
          The behavior that produces blown sessions is observable in real time. Re-entry pace shortens. Stops get widened. Sizing creeps up. Every one of these is measurable from the order stream NinjaTrader is already producing — no one had built the software to extract those signals and feed them back to the trader during the session.
        </p>
        <p class="font-semibold text-zinc-900">
          So we did.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="border-t border-zinc-100"></div>

  <!-- What we are -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-emerald-700 uppercase mb-4">What We Are</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 leading-snug">
        Behavioral risk infrastructure for NinjaTrader 8.
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
        <p>
          Meridian is a NinjaTrader 8 add-on that monitors seven behavioral signals from your live order activity and surfaces a Psychological Stability Index (PSI) in real time. <a href="/guard" class="text-emerald-700 underline hover:text-emerald-900">Meridian Guard</a> adds a configurable enforcement layer — alerts, acknowledgment prompts, mandatory countdowns, entry blocks, broker disconnect — when the patterns you defined as off-limits start to appear.
        </p>
        <p>
          We are not a trading guru. We do not sell signals, courses, mentorship, or Discord access. We are a small team building one thing: behavioral risk infrastructure for active discretionary futures traders on NinjaTrader 8.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="border-t border-zinc-100"></div>

  <!-- Official Ecosystem Vendor -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-emerald-700 uppercase mb-4">Official NinjaTrader Ecosystem Vendor</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 leading-snug">
        Reviewed, tested, and approved by NinjaTrader.
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
        <p>
          Meridian is an <strong class="text-zinc-900">Official NinjaTrader Ecosystem Vendor</strong>. Our company, our website, our social channels, and the Meridian NT8 add-on itself were reviewed and approved by NinjaTrader&rsquo;s Compliance, QA, and Executive teams before being listed in the official Ecosystem.
        </p>
        <p>
          That review covered: signed Vendor Listing Agreement, executive background check, full compliance audit of every public surface where we talk about trading, and a hands-on QA pass on the live NT8 add-on by NinjaTrader&rsquo;s internal QA team.
        </p>
        <p>
          Practically, this means two things for our users. First, the product you install is the same product NinjaTrader&rsquo;s own team installed and tested. Second, the public claims we make about Meridian have already cleared the global retail-trading compliance bar that NinjaTrader applies to every Ecosystem vendor &mdash; not just to us.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">
          NinjaTrader® is a registered trademark of NinjaTrader LLC. Meridian is operated by an independent company and is a third-party add-on for NinjaTrader 8; it is not owned by NinjaTrader LLC.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="border-t border-zinc-100"></div>

  <!-- What we are not -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-zinc-50/60">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-emerald-700 uppercase mb-4">What We Are Not</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 leading-snug">
        We don't publish track records. The product is the work.
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
        <p>
          We are not a hedge fund running our own strategy. We do not publish account statements, screenshots of "I made $X this month," or any other form of personal P&amp;L marketing. The product is the work; the work is the marketing.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you want trading signals, we are not the right product. If you want a journaling platform, we are not the right product. If you want a risk tool that watches for the <em>behavior</em> that produces the loss — not the loss itself — Meridian is purpose-built for that.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="border-t border-zinc-100"></div>

  <!-- How we operate -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-emerald-700 uppercase mb-4">How We Operate</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 leading-snug">
        Local-first. Public roadmap. Direct support.
      </h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-base list-disc pl-5 marker:text-emerald-600">
        <li>All session data stays on your machine. There is no cloud backend, no telemetry, no behavioral data ever leaves your PC.</li>
        <li>The product is sold via Whop with a 7-day free trial.</li>
        <li>Updates ship publicly via the <a href="/download" class="text-emerald-700 underline hover:text-emerald-900">changelog</a>. v1.2.0 is the current release.</li>
        <li>Support questions go to <a href="mailto:contactmeridianpsi@gmail.com" class="text-emerald-700 underline hover:text-emerald-900">contactmeridianpsi@gmail.com</a> and are answered within 24 hours.</li>
        <li>The team is small. Every change to the product is reviewed by someone who understands both the trading workflow and the code.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-6 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
        If you have feedback, a bug report, or a feature request — send it. We read every email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PSI scope — behavioral proxy -->
  <section class="py-12 px-6 bg-zinc-50/80 border-t border-zinc-100">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">
        PSI is a behavioral proxy index derived from your trading activity inside NinjaTrader. It does not measure physiology (for example heart rate or stress hormones), and it is not validated as a predictor of trading profits or losses. Meridian is designed to improve self-awareness and discipline during a session; outcomes still depend on many factors beyond psychology.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white border-t border-zinc-100 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-3">Try it free for 7 days.</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 text-base mb-8">Cancel any time during the trial.</p>
      <a
        href="/pricing"
        class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full transition-colors"
      >
        Start free trial — 7 days
      </a>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-zinc-400">$49.99/month after trial · NinjaTrader 8 required</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
